tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Biofuel_Efficiency_Data (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  research_id INT,
  biofuel_type TEXT,
  conversion_efficiency FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (research_id) REFERENCES Biofuel_Conversion_Research(research_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Biofuel_Research_Experiments (
  experiment_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_date DATE,
  biofuel_type VARCHAR(50),
  conversion_technique VARCHAR(50),
  efficiency DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Research_Techniques (
  technique_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  technique_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE,
  description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Researchers (
  researcher_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  researcher_name VARCHAR(50),
  affiliation TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Experiment_Results (
  result_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id INT REFERENCES Biofuel_Research_Experiments(experiment_id),
  technique_id INT REFERENCES Research_Techniques(technique_id),
  result_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Research_Publications (
  publication_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  publication_title VARCHAR(100),
  publication_date DATE,
  researcher_id INT REFERENCES Researchers(researcher_id)
)
